text: Alain Cacheux (November 15, 1947 – July 26, 2020) was a French politician. He was a member of the National Assembly of France from 1997 to 2002 and again from 2007 to 2012. He represented the Nord department. He was a member of the Socialiste, radical, citoyen et divers gauche.
